(24, 1, '2021-04-13 13:15:49', '2021-04-13 13:15:49', '<p>This is a default Services page, Which comes preinstalled with HostingRaja\'s WordPress Hosting.<br />If you want to edit the content, Please login to admin section (refer your welcome email for username and password).<br />Once you log in, Go to Page and then click on Services Page. Modify the pages as you wish and then click on Publish and Update option. Your new page will be reflected for customers.</p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How To Create a New Services</strong> <strong>pages</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Step 1 :</strong> Login your wp-admin dashboard, ( you can login wp-admin dashboard from ClientArea  <strong>or</strong> https://example.com/wp-admin ).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Step 2 :</strong>  Click the Pages in side bar.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Step 3 :</strong> Now select the <strong>Services</strong> and click the <strong>edit</strong> option.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":172,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://jegandemowev.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/wppages4-1024x472.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-172\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Step 4 :</strong> Now edit your service pages and update it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":173,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://jegandemowev.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/wppages5-1024x439.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-173\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator